# PSTG Markdown Extensions

Custom Markdown extensions for the *Plain Storage Tech Guide* (PSTG) project.

## Features
*   `=text=` : Creates a spoiler blur effect.
*   `[text]<style>` : Applies custom inline styles (e.g., `[text]<red>`).
